		<content_encoded><![CDATA[We're soliciting stories about workplace theft for a journal that will appear in early April, in honor of <a href="http://stealfromwork.crimethinc.com/">STEAL SOMETHING FROM WORK DAY</a>. Obviously, they should be anonymous and fictionalized. A simple paragraph will suffice, though if one of you sends in the <em>War and Peace</em> of employee revenge, we won't complain.

Send stories to <a href="mailto:stealfromworkday@gmail.com">stealfromworkday@gmail.com</a>. The deadline is Tuesday, March 30.]]></content_encoded>
